extendedInfo.description: Hi ~ everyone~This game is a casual game that can enjoy fun without the burden of all agesBecause of a similar operation like Angry Bird, You can easily enjoy this game.Does not require a lot of time while enjoying the game and this is a good way to relieve your stress.Unbelievably good goals feel will make you crazy..If you like basketball Don't hesitate.If you do not like basketball, Enjoy ~If you do not want to play basketball.. this is not a basketball.just join now! feel free ../////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////Game StoryTraveling with a basket.Travel all over the world with a basket containing many ballsVarious difficult challenges will be awaiting for you during your travel.Always death and the fight against financial crisis, Wall Street Even eagle can not drink a sip of water, SaharaSanta is Fun, Fun,Fun in the summer ,LaplandSad story of underwater city , AtlantisThe end of travel is a beautiful planet, The MoonJoin in these fantasy world ~Travel the fantasy world having various obstacles and difficult climatic conditions(different gravity and different wind condition)You can be a goal scorer who conquered all.Have a good luck!  :)
